#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn55.37"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.37:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.37:0.2"
msgid "4. Puññābhisandavagga "
msgstr "4. Overflowing Merit "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.37:0.3"
msgid "37. Mahānāmasutta "
msgstr "37. With Mahānāma "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.395, sc1
msgctxt "sn55.37:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ nigrodhārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Sakyans, near Kapilavatthu in the Banyan Tree Monastery. "

msgctxt "sn55.37:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho mahānāmo sakko yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho mahānāmo sakko bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Mahānāma the Sakyan went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn55.37:2.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, upāsako hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, how is a lay follower defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.37:2.2"
msgid "“Yato kho, mahānāma, buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gato hoti, dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ gato hoti, saṅghaṃ saraṇaṃ gato hoti—"
msgstr "“Mahānāma, when you’ve gone for refuge to the Buddha, the teaching, and the Saṅgha, "

msgctxt "sn55.37:2.3"
msgid "ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako hotī”ti. "
msgstr "you’re considered to be a lay follower.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn55.37:3.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, upāsako sīlasampanno hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“But how is an ethical lay follower defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.37:3.2"
msgid "“Yato kho, mahānāma, upāsako pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti, kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti, musāvādā paṭivirato hoti, surāmerayamajjappamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato hoti—"
msgstr "“When a lay follower doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, or consume alcoholic drinks that cause negligence, "

msgctxt "sn55.37:3.3"
msgid "ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako sīlasampanno hotī”ti. "
msgstr "they’re considered to be an ethical lay follower.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn55.37:4.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, upāsako saddhāsampanno hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“But how is a faithful lay follower defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.37:4.2"
msgid "“Idha, mahānāma, upāsako saddho hoti, saddahati tathāgatassa bodhiṃ—"
msgstr "“It’s when a lay follower has faith in the Realized One’s awakening: "

msgctxt "sn55.37:4.3"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr "‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme guide for those who wish to train, teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’ "

msgctxt "sn55.37:4.4"
msgid "Ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako saddhāsampanno hotī”ti. "
msgstr "Then they’re considered to be a faithful lay follower.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn55.37:5.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, upāsako cāgasampanno hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“But how is a generous lay follower defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.37:5.2"
msgid "“Idha, mahānāma, upāsako vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati muttacāgo payatapāṇi vossaggarato yācayogo dānasaṃvibhāgarato—"
msgstr "“It’s when a lay follower lives at home rid of the stain of stinginess, freely generous, open-handed, loving to let go, committed to charity, loving to give and to share. "

msgctxt "sn55.37:5.3"
msgid "ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako cāgasampanno hotī”ti. "
msgstr "Then they’re considered to be a generous lay follower.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn55.37:6.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, upāsako paññāsampanno hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“But how is a wise lay follower defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.37:6.2"
msgid "“Idha, mahānāma, upāsako paññavā hoti udayatthagāminiyā paññāya samannāgato ariyāya nibbedhikāya sammā dukkhakkhayagāminiyā—"
msgstr "“It’s when a lay follower is wise. They have the wisdom of arising and passing away which is noble, penetrative, and leads to the complete ending of suffering. "

msgctxt "sn55.37:6.3"
msgid "ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako paññāsampanno hotī”ti. "
msgstr "Then they’re considered to be a wise lay follower.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.37:6.4"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

